@startuml
title Adapter - Ejemplo 1 - Implementacion Generica
left to right direction
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam class {
  BackgroundColor #F8FAFC
  BorderColor #334155
  ArrowColor #334155
  FontColor #0F172A
}
hide empty members

package "main" #EEF2FF {
  class Main <<cliente>>
}

package "pattern" #ECFDF5 {
  class Adapter {
    +request(int normalizedValue): void
  }
  class Client {
    +execute(): void
  }
  class LegacyService {
    +specificRequest(double externalValue): void
  }
  interface Target <<interfaz>> {
  }
}

Target <|.. Adapter
Main ..> Adapter : ejecuta

note bottom
La implementacion esta concentrada en src/pattern/PatternImplementation.java.
Main solo instancia y ejecuta el caso de uso.
end note
@enduml
